metadata.name: E-Chill #0001
metadata.description:
《Elysium Chill》 is based on the original Elysium Shell character modeling and costume with extended changes.

The first step is to turn the original delicate face into a crooked ugly face as much as you can imagine.

The second step is to scramble all the cool accessories to make them look like the knock-off in the night market.

The third step is to turn all 3D model into low-poly, low-quality, and low-reduction.

Finally, if it is a version with pets, we turn it into an alien Chihuahua.

More about 《Elysium Chill》 : 

https://medium.com/@pupupupuisland.eth/wtf-who-made-this-shitty-version-of-elysium-shell-205547d831bb
